{
  "stem": "3040.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They got heart attacks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And some people got killed by them because they didn't like the way they moved, or how fast the moved.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In fact, my mother-in-law, the mother of my first wife, got a stroke at that day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And a few days later, she died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it's definitely attributable to this incidence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was terror.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sight of the Germans in their uniforms-- and these were very neatly dressed Germans, the SS mostly, or the [NON-ENGLISH] which is the SD which it is [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very good looking young men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And very well neatly dressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to us, they were like monsters, because they brought with them this terror that they were projecting wherever they came, particularly in regard to Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we knew what they want from Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew their-- what their intentions are.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a terrible incidence that happened in December.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then life went back almost to normal under the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had this chocolate factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had some raw materials.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started by ourselves without employing anybody to produce, to make chocolate, to make the product from it, and to be able to sustain ourselves and to sell it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then about-- this must have been the beginning of March in 1940, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we still had this factory.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We still had some raw materials to work with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then a young German in civilian clothes came in, and he produced papers that he is going to take-- he was assigned by the German government to take over the factory.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They called it [SPEAKING GERMAN], the one who was not for himself, so to speak, but he was representing the German government.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
